[11:51:07.808] [INFO ]     Okay, here's the information regarding the NovaAI 401(k) match and eligibility:
    
    **401(k) Match:**
    
    NovaAI offers a 100% match on the first 6% of employee contributions to the 401(k). This means that for every dollar you contribute up to 6% of your salary, NovaAI will contribute one dollar on your behalf.
    
    **Eligibility:**
    
    You are eligible to participate in the NovaAI 401(k) plan after **30 days** of employment. 
    
    If you have any further questions, please don't hesitate to ask! You can also find more detailed information in the employee handbook or by contacting the HR department directly.
