[11:51:07.809] [INFO ]   Q: What is the annual L&D budget per employee and how does it work?
[11:51:07.809] [INFO ] ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━
