    **NovaGuard Advanced Pricing:**
    
    The pricing for NovaGuard Advanced is custom and depends on your specific needs and usage. It's not a fixed price. To get a precise quote, you need to contact our sales team directly. 
    
    You can reach them through this link: [https://nova.ai/contact-sales/](https://nova.ai/contact-sales/)
    
    **Model Monitoring Limits:**
    
    The model monitoring limits for NovaGuard Advanced are also customized based on the number of models you want to monitor and the volume of data you're analyzing. 
    
    Generally, NovaGuard Advanced allows monitoring of **up to 100 models** simultaneously. However, the number of data points monitored per model is variable and determined by the complexity of the model and your specific agreement. 
    
    For detailed information about the specific limits applicable to your account, please refer to your contract or reach out to your NovaAI account manager.
    
    **Important Note:** Pricing and feature availability are subject to change. Always confirm the latest details with the sales team or your account manager.
